on   date november   citation  ny slip op  docket number  justia opinion summary defendant was convicted of attempted murder in the second degree assault in the first degree reckless endangerment in the first degree and criminal possession of a weapon in the second and third degrees defendant’s c people v golo   date november   citation  ny slip op  docket number  justia opinion summary in  defendant pleaded guilty to criminal possession of a controlled substance in the third degree later that year defendant pleaded guilty to two counts each of robbery in the first degree and of endangering the w hawkins v berlin   date november   citation  ny slip op  docket number  justia opinion summary beginning in  petitioner received public assistance from new york city department of social services petitioner gave birth to a son michael the next year michael was added to petitioner’s public assistance case bennett v st johns home date november   citation  ny slip op  docket number  ssm  carver v state   date november   citation  ny slip op  docket number  justia opinion summary in  petitioner began receiving public assistance from the city of new york at that time the city required that petitioner work thirtyfive hours per week in the work experience program wep in  petitioner sierra club v village of painted post   date november   citation  ny slip op  docket number  justia opinion summary petitioners including individual residents of the village of painted post commenced this ny cplr  proceeding against the village and others collectively respondents asserting that the village failed to comp people v wragg   date november   citation  ny slip op  docket number  justia opinion summary after a jury trial defendant was convicted of sexual assault in the first degree the trial court sentenced defendant as a second child sexual assault felony offender to a determinate term of fifteen years with five yea people v matthew p   date november   citation  ny slip op  docket number  jus